            "text": "{\"reviews\":[{\"ratingId\":\"e384c8d4-1306-49ef-b99b-2b0de7d953ab\",\"rating\":\"STAR_4_5\",\"review\":\"The movie that started the MCU.  Still a great movie to this day, mainly thanks to Robert Downey Jr charisma that frankly I don't think anyone could top.  The action scenes as Iron Man aren't quite as cool as in the sequels and the avengers, but it was a start, so you can forgive it a little.\",\"displayName\":\"Jorge A\",\"initials\":\"JA\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-04-10T02:35:25.503Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"6xMi29sv1h4nhE2UYwU6nSeNS33cYAiWjsAbSjAH22cWQt53szxcVzhmmcOjuVzU9mI3jIggcb7SPxcoxSEJFKvCB7ikvs6Lcd4sRnSpJcBG\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"A\",\"givenName\":\"Jorge\",\"fullName\":\"Jorge A\",\"profileImage\":null,\"profileHandle\":\"RT50429328\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"JA\",\"displayName\":\"Jorge A\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"6abbff46-14b8-41ea-97d9-b9ca726bea32\",\"rating\":\"STAR_4\",\"review\":\"Phenomenal origin story and character development of Tony stark from being a money hungry careless billionaire to becoming a real hero. The betrayal of Obadiah is a great story that builds and shocks audiences. Overall a great movie and the best way to kick off the MCU.\",\"displayName\":\"Weston A.\",\"initials\":\"WA\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-04-06T17:27:46.099Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"GeVsNKubEIkmS7LFA5HnMu5PuNNcGdtWXsVOsBoUaacWztdjU7nujncXXcx8FaVSLJf1GUAAcVKtdPu4Pt2zsOVU4RcYNu4kHv6IGoSe1ubE\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"Arbogast\",\"givenName\":\"Weston\",\"fullName\":\"Weston Arbogast\",\"profileImage\":null,\"profileHandle\":\"THEmoviereviewerWZA\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"WA\",\"displayName\":\"Weston A\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"3f82ef0d-46aa-4069-89e2-1d00c4b7d562\",\"rating\":\"STAR_4\",\"review\":\"Pretty good story I felt like it was well paced and I love the character as I’m watching the timeline for the first time\",\"displayName\":\"Morgan L.\",\"initials\":\"ML\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-04-06T13:56:11.435Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"oo1h1RheNH8au0gCDQs4RFo6UPPcaWSxLH95FWVummc7Xt1BsVPuOXfYYcYKFvDfg3hwgFbbc2quLbF6dFYwcL8uXPspjhkeHD9FXWtEahMd\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"Leach\",\"givenName\":\"Morgan\",\"fullName\":\"Morgan Leach\",\"profileImage\":\"https://images.fandango.com/cms/assets/099bc600-949f-11f0-8321-2b978811c524--rt-app-studioavatars-starwars.png\",\"profileHandle\":\"Oofmorgan\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"ML\",\"displayName\":\"Morgan L\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"547cf7fe-5367-4fe0-9afb-70dd3f71fb3d\",\"rating\":\"STAR_4_5\",\"review\":\"Amazing movie showing Tony starks arrogance in a perfect manor and the twist of Obidah stane being a villian is great the final fight left something to be desired but an almost perfect origin story I highly recommend it \",\"displayName\":\"John F\",\"initials\":\"JF\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-04-03T12:11:54.811Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"49mtGYuv9uDXFnBuWJtQJUNGcoocBOHAVfdOIO7uNNc13tDKU1VS5KFNNcYvFvKUw6FDkI66cKxhYJf2ASvOuKeFY1tP4H7ds43hNzs7BH94\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"Faloon\",\"givenName\":\"John\",\"fullName\":\"John Faloon\",\"profileImage\":null,\"profileHandle\":\"Faloon\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"JF\",\"displayName\":\"John F\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"7a66abe8-95aa-4e8c-b611-b16f3589424f\",\"rating\":\"STAR_5\",\"review\":\"RDJ perfomance as Tony Stark was impecable. Loved the arrogant, annoying multimillionaire on screens. The fight scenes were PACKED in action, and not to say about the stunning visual effects. I heard this movie was a huge gamble from MCU to run from bankruptcy, and oh boy, that was the best gamble they could ever do.\",\"displayName\":\"Guilherme M\",\"initials\":\"GM\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-04-02T21:28:20.662Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"wkbHPAU8pCaQFxJFYVIOeu4WhEEcqQFXwS7WUEpi66cpVtRKCOjsakHLLckqud7FgKtYdFPPcqDI3mfLgu9BivLCoGc8NhPwsBOhmquxjH58\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"Mendes\",\"givenName\":\"Guilherme\",\"fullName\":\"Guilherme Mendes\",\"profileImage\":null,\"profileHandle\":\"RT21202523\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"GM\",\"displayName\":\"Guilherme M\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"a8689ce5-dfe3-4f39-a50d-11cbcacc617f\",\"rating\":\"STAR_5\",\"review\":\"Tony stark was able to build this shi in a cave. \",\"displayName\":\"Intellectual G.\",\"initials\":\"IG\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-04-01T03:31:08.707Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"jWatWnU7WIeKuEpfQbI12sknhvvcKoHm5uO0HNMUVVcG4tmYiJ4f3JTAAcBvHXGsALhbKf33cXQIO7U7piApH3zhB7sKGcLVFdOFk8IgGI74\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"God\",\"givenName\":\"Intellectual\",\"fullName\":\"Intellectual God\",\"profileImage\":\"https://images.fandango.com/cms/assets/dc347580-2f50-11f0-a07e-5b03d6159fe4--rt-app-profileavatar-neon-vh.png\",\"profileHandle\":\"Intellectual\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"IG\",\"displayName\":\"Intellectual G\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"8b646efa-ab91-4fe9-8683-54da342fbf94\",\"rating\":\"STAR_4_5\",\"review\":\"Reviewed 5/14/2022\\n\\nWell, I'm glad to see that Marvel's Cinematic Universe hit the ground running. The main character has a very clear and well thought out arc, and Obadiah Stane is well... Obadiah Stane. I think the plot twist of him selling weapons to the terrorists so that they can kill Tony Stark so that he can rule the company is a bit convoluted, though there have been worse villain ploys. His reveal as being evil feels like an afterthought, the rest of the movie works so well and then suddenly Stane is a bad guy. That's really my only complaint about the movie. If it had a better villain and a more coherent way if revealing said villain, it'd be higher up. The rest of the film is still incredible.\",\"displayName\":\"Jacob L.\",\"initials\":\"JL\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-04-01T02:08:24.431Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"xjkUvBtGjtXzh9BsdYFoMSLBhEEc4gUaghXRcV6sLLc6qt8pFoguDJhjjcKNiKLfXqixkt22cgWh7asgEIkaSJ7UMGSkYh3MFdESvBFAzf1g\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"Linares\",\"givenName\":\"Jacob\",\"fullName\":\"Jacob Linares\",\"profileImage\":null,\"profileHandle\":\"DerpyIsMLG\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"JL\",\"displayName\":\"Jacob L\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"edd16b20-be97-4287-bc93-808aef1b5ee7\",\"rating\":\"STAR_4_5\",\"review\":\"I am just starting the MCU series and this is a great initial movie of this big chain of films. The concept of this movie is unimaginable.\",\"displayName\":\"yanzi S\",\"initials\":\"YS\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-03-22T20:25:41.875Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"ngOce2IvkFOEFLvU0LF6wH1mHzzc3BtW4tgjsoNt77cvAt2ASogCMWsbbcpNhnzuPzu8bteecW5CYQUmNF25sqYsa5snVhzvuB5uBMFEmFgx\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"shen\",\"givenName\":\"yanzi\",\"fullName\":\"yanzi shen\",\"profileImage\":null,\"profileHandle\":\"Yuirxya\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"YS\",\"displayName\":\"yanzi S\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"3667826e-f1c7-4ccf-803f-d69e94f8f028\",\"rating\":\"STAR_4\",\"review\":\"Iron Man Review\\nIt’s hard to believe that this movie started the MCU all those years ago. But after rewatching it, it’s obvious how this movie spawned the MCU. This movie is great! This is helped by Robert Downey Jr.’s great performance. It’s been said a million times but it’s still true: RDJ was born to play Tony Stark! I love how we see Tony grow from an arrogant playboy to an actual hero with great intentions. The armor is also great in this movie. We are at a stage in the MCU that’s pre-nanotech, which makes it more believable. The armor is more raw and believable because we see each piece slide and come together, whereas the nanotech borderlines magic. I also think that Obadiah Stane is an alright villain. He’s not like a top 10 MCU villain, but he’s pretty good for this movie. I also love the action scenes. The scene where he breaks out of the cave, the final Iron Man vs. Iron Monger fight, they’re all great! Overall, this is an amazing movie that is a great MCU kickoff!\",\"displayName\":\"Bret M.\",\"initials\":\"BM\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-03-22T11:42:35.661Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"JzkfG9SW9HPpUBDFkGu1VfdWI77cRMtVAcBJFNPfNNcRetbVhM6f8YFDDckwuwQh5qSjdI33cQRsgVF76Cw2C7ES63HV5HQEsN7I39u6wHQ8\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"Morton\",\"givenName\":\"Bret\",\"fullName\":\"Bret Morton\",\"profileImage\":\"https://images.fandango.com/cms/assets/099bc600-949f-11f0-8321-2b978811c524--rt-app-studioavatars-starwars.png\",\"profileHandle\":\"BretM-3\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"BM\",\"displayName\":\"Bret M\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}},{\"ratingId\":\"9f4c2144-44ee-45a7-a034-4dbd09db828b\",\"rating\":\"STAR_4_5\",\"review\":\"probabaly the best movie of it's time\\n\",\"displayName\":\"Rakesh Y\",\"initials\":\"RY\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isSuperReviewer\":false,\"hasSpoilers\":false,\"hasProfanity\":false,\"createDate\":\"2026-03-20T06:54:13.063Z\",\"user\":{\"encryptedUserId\":\"XjOFdoCgxuXwUV8IW2Sp3sGJSVVcoxtMRtx6SMPFOOcNotoNsRXuvVIeecdLF7MFdaHzPI11c8Qi7NIARsxQFpWFgdIqpIQ4HJ8F7RFkphpa\",\"realm\":\"RT\",\"familyName\":\"Y\",\"givenName\":\"Rakesh\",\"fullName\":\"Rakesh Y\",\"profileImage\":null,\"profileHandle\":\"RT33041687\",\"background\":null,\"initials\":\"RY\",\"displayName\":\"Rakesh Y\"},\"reactionSummary\":{\"reactions\":[],\"totalCount\":0},\"audienceScore\":{\"isActivelyModerated\":false}}],\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":true,\"hasPreviousPage\":false,\"endCursor\":\"eyJyZWFsbV91c2VySWQiOiJSVF84ZDczMTIwMi00NDI4LTQwNzEtYjg2MS1iZTBiODExNmI4OTMiLCJlbXNJZCI6IjQxY2EwMDZiLTg4MjAtMzc5Yy04NGZjLWFhYWU4NzBiMzdmNiIsImVtc0lkX2hhc1Jldmlld0lzVmlzaWJsZSI6IjQxY2EwMDZiLTg4MjAtMzc5Yy04NGZjLWFhYWU4NzBiMzdmNl9UIiwiY3JlYXRlRGF0ZSI6IjIwMjYtMDMtMjBUMDY6NTQ6MTMuMDYzWiJ9\"}}"
          },
